channel.description:
Thanks for visiting my channel! I'm Amir, professional 3D animator, creator of Real Data.
The process of every animation video on my channel takes me over 96 hours. To make it short,for people asking how i make videos here are the primary steps :
Step 1 ‚Äì Research for the best content idea. Step 2 ‚Äì Collecting items for each video, adjusting and trimming videos using adobe premiere pro and cutting out images using adobe Photoshop. Step 3 ‚Äì Putting together a creative approach that satisfies viewers. Step 4 ‚Äì Animating and adding movement using (blender 3d software) to the story and make it more powerful.
People looking to steal my content:
If you want to use my videos elsewhere for educational purposes, drop me a line. I am alerted about stolen videos every day thanks to my subscribers. I am actively submitting copyright infringements on YT, FB, IG. Sad.
I encourage you to search for interesting idea and create your own unique videos.
